name: Dumble
description: Dumbbells are often used for joint-isolation exercises such as biceps curls, chest flyes or shoulder raises.

name: Treadmill
description: As a form of cardio exercise, using a treadmill is an excellent way of burning calories and losing weight.

name: Rope
description: Push into the balls of your feet and extend your legs as you lift the ropes with both arms over your shoulders.

name: Pull Up
description: In addition to working your back, pull-ups strengthen and sculpt your shoulders, forearms, and chest (pecs).

name: Push Up
description: The push-up helps to build muscle and improve strength throughout the upper body.

name: Squat
description: Squats burn calories and might help you lose weight.
